        # Iterate over each element in the array

            if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
                arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]
                swapped = True
        
        # If no swaps were made during iteration, then the array is already sorted
        if not swapped:
            break
    
    return arr
